_sText:
cs_concert is a port of the cs_concert map from the Counter-Strike: Global Offensive game.



Description:

- The American dream is under attack! Anarchists have decided to crash a country rock festival and take the stars hostage.

It's up to the FBI to rescue these local treasures to restore freedom in the United States of America!

- Hostage Rescue Scenario

- Special thanks to the MapCore Community for all the support.
